{"categories":["computer-internet","notification","marketing-and-design"],"collections":"","description":"This email template is designed to engage audiences in the Software and Technology sector, with a creative approach towards GDPR-compliant resubscription requests. The template is perfect for notification and marketing purposes, smartly prompting users to opt in again and resubscribe to your services. It effectively communicates the benefits of staying connected, while ensuring transparency about the terms of service. With a clear call-to-action, it encourages users to renew their subscription, thereby enhancing customer retention. This template serves as an excellent tactic to maintain an open line of communication with your subscribers while adhering to data protection regulations.","short_description":"Experience a blend of creativity and GDPR compliance with our email template. Encourage users to resubscribe, perfect for software and technology businesses. Simplifies re-subscription and aligns with GDPR through an easy-to-understand terms of service. Ideal for notification and marketing purposes, transforming opting in again into an engaging experience. Enhance your subscription strategy today.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/galina-grahovska.jpg","description":"I have gained experience and skills in communications and organization of the work while I was hired in E.Miroglio EAD. I’ve also got excellent French as I was living in France for a few years.\r\n\r\nAbout an year ago, I’ve started designing interfaces and that’s definitely what I was looking for my whole life. I’m using Adobe Photoshop to design websites, emails and mobile apps. I also create prototypes in InVision to make the whole process from the start to the finish much easier.","short_description":"","display_name":"Galina Grahovska","id":"galina-grahovska"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:sche